properties.areaDesc: Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 11 at 3:36PM AKST until January 13 at 12:00PM AKST by NWS Fairbanks, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow and blowing snow with low visibility expected. Plan
on difficult travel conditions. Total snow accumulations of 2 to
4 inches are expected. Visibility will be one half mile or less
at times.

* WHERE...Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills.

* WHEN...Noon Sunday to noon Monday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strong winds are occuring tonight and will
continue into Monday. Falling snow will develop Sunday afternoon
and continue into Monday. The lowest visibility will be Sunday
through Monday.
properties.instruction:
A Winter Weather Advisory for snow means periods of snow will
cause travel difficulties.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON SUNDAY TO NOON AKST MONDAY
